  <span id="freeText6388570532367191338" style="display:none">After reading the synopsis I couldn't wait to get this book, but when I finally got it I was very disappointed. I dont mean to be rude, but I cannot even understand how this book got such high ratings. I tried to read it five times and each time I just had to put it down. The book just didn't pull me in, I mean the characters did't have any real personality and it all seemed so predictable. Maybe the story got better as you went further, but I just didn't have it in me to keep reading. The overall plot was good but the writing seemed a little amateur to me.</span>
