<li class='cover' id='bookCover_13596166'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13596166-joyland"><img alt="Joyland" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1348154483l/13596166._SX98_.jpg" />
